column3: CREATE DATABASE `inventory` CHARSET utf8mb4 COLLATE utf8mb4_0900_ai_ci

CREATE TABLE `sales` (
  `usergender` mediumtext,
  `usercity` mediumtext,
  `usersentiment` int DEFAULT NULL,
  `zipcode` mediumtext,
  `sku` mediumtext,
  `createdate` varchar(64) NOT NULL,
  `category` mediumtext,
  `price` decimal(12,5) DEFAULT NULL,
  `county` mediumtext,
  `countycode` mediumtext,
  `userstate` mediumtext,
  `categorygroup` mediumtext,
  PRIMARY KEY (`createdate`)
) ENGINE=InnoDB DEFAULT CHARSET=utf8mb4 COLLATE=utf8mb4_0900_ai_ci
